<plot>Enter the netherworld of an emotionally damaged but ambitious actress, a modern-day "Every Woman" besieged by male corruption and betrayed by the dysfunction of her own instincts. Join her in a turbo charged spiral into a bottomless barrel of despair, pain, hate and humility. One mis-step follows another, across a bridge from grim reality to an even more disturbing psychological landscape as creepy as it is violent. A close up view of our current world, out of order, minus the psych meds.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?594161</url></doc>
